{"tid":2252893,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 12藍色實機曝光　內地網民不滿色差大揚言退貨：似底褲藍","createTime":"2020-10-21T19:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T14:52:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dcdcf4eac2054a86ea4696140636d850501e02f5","tid":2252893,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T19:57:58.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司日前推出首款支援5G網絡的iPhone 12 系列手機，上周五（16日）開售，最快本周五（23日）便可以入手。不過有部份樣辦貨被偷步進行開箱， iPhone 12和iPhone 12 Pro的實機相片和影片已經在網上流傳。<br />\n<br />\n其中最受關注的莫過於藍色版iPhone 12，不少內地網民都哀嚎，實機相片顯示的鮮豔藍色與官方宣傳照的灰藍色相比，顏色相差實在太多，紛紛吐槽iPhone 12的藍色是「內褲藍」，有已經下單的買家更揚言會退貨。<br />\n<br />\n各種開箱影片廣傳後，「iPhone 12藍色」一度成為微博熱搜榜首位。iPhone 12 Pro暗色系的海藍色則成為網民比較的對象，不少人認為藍色機身的iPhone 12 Pro看起來更加內斂和神秘，但又不失尊貴，而藍色版iPhone 12卻因為顏色太鮮豔顯得庸俗。許多網民甚至顏色相似的內褲、垃圾桶、拖鞋拿出來作對比。<br />\n<br />\n內地知名數碼博主「龍二Pro」也在微博發文詢問，「感覺翻車了，開始猶豫要不要退貨了！有人來勸勸我嗎？有沒有別的什麼同色系的藍色，寓意好一點的，發出來安慰一下？」這則帖文吸引了18萬人點讚和2萬5千多人留言。想退貨的網民表示：「我好糾結，要不要退了換個綠的」、「藍色真的這麼絕望嗎，我需要退貨重新拍了」、「買了藍色的我，看一次想退貨一次」、「要真是那個塑料藍，就非常想令人退貨」。<br />\n<br />\n不過也有人指出，實機相或許是「拍攝者的相機問題」。還有網民表示，雖然看到這麼多人退貨，但他選擇不退，「等我拿到機子現實中上手再說。萬一到時候見到實機有反轉真香定律怎麼辦呢，既然買了還不如看看真機，不跟風。」<br />\n<br />\n其他網民熱議：<br />\n「不買褲衩藍誰知道你換新手機了。」<br />\n「誰買新顏色是為了『好看』啊，都是為了『容易看見』啊。」<br />\n「現在嫌棄得要死，事後炒得更高。」<br />\n「藍色妖機。」<br />\n「挺好看的，怎麼都說不好看。」<br />\n「反正要套手機殼。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201021/395618370113769472658024.png/Vh-CWXAb3B5kunE5KuuUDpwzjzSpDrQXC7Wmpwu1pqc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201021%2F395618370113769472658024.png%2FVh-CWXAb3B5kunE5KuuUDpwzjzSpDrQXC7Wmpwu1pqc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1b039c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201021/395618944389484544602893.png/bhwK9cFyeUkP22zkFmC27J8QTYVai1SuHXvaMR172jE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201021%2F395618944389484544602893.png%2FbhwK9cFyeUkP22zkFmC27J8QTYVai1SuHXvaMR172jE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=51dab87f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201021/395617782248509440967138.jpeg/b4ose83vgPLKxUAP7VTb4a7hOuH3oxFyiP1egYj9XoE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201021%2F395617782248509440967138.jpeg%2Fb4ose83vgPLKxUAP7VTb4a7hOuH3oxFyiP1egYj9XoE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=4b30b99d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55f0135b1b053d81f7f6947b97c320396d881e78","tid":2252893,"uid":145307,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T20:49:02.000Z","msg":"口裏說不 咪又係個撚個死去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9893cd57a38b78f1d579c5aae6642b2ee71ded","tid":2252893,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T21:52:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得得白色接受到"},{"pid":"a34e8641918c472eb45f4b895ad135af0ff14a1a","tid":2252893,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:00:18.000Z","msg":"中國人又爆買iPhone，真係愛<del>美</del>國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Unknown-1-5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FUnknown-1-5.png&h=77e3b4b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a2f7dd5e668a5d9720fca38e03dce1f534cb7eb","tid":2252893,"uid":49664,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mysunny.com.tw/upload/Product/4019030001/201908201336291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mysunny.com.tw%2Fupload%2FProduct%2F4019030001%2F201908201336291.jpg&h=59436a86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a6896f878534af1dd7cf4b56dba35ea5575a72e","tid":2252893,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a2f7dd5e668a5d9720fca38e03dce1f534cb7eb","tid":2252893,"uid":49664,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score"